cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SY, cs.DM

The paper deals with the construction of a neural network model for electricity consumption forecasting, which falls under the category of machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. The use of particle swarm optimization (PSO) and backpropagation (BP) algorithms also suggests that the paper could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). Additionally, the use of historical data and simulation for forecasting could also place the paper under cs.DM (Data Mining).
